Objective
===============
A distributed set of servers that helps in getting files from anywhere

Features & Requirements
==============================
1. Standalone server
2. Search files by different parameters, e.g. name, size, date
3. Each server has a set of input source where the search is done.
    A. Input source can be: 
          I. Local folder
         II. Another FileAnywhere server 
    B. An input source can be mirror on different server.
          I. A mirror can have a subset of files only.
         II. A mirror can start empty and act as a proxy for other mirrors, 
             caching files as they are being requested.
4. The server should be private and a secure token is required to get or search
    files.
5. File is identity by [FileAnywere_Server_ID : SOURCE_ID : File_PATH]